After participating in <lj user="9thmoon"/> 's poll asking if others fold their undies &amp; hung their shirts in a specific way, I want to know what kind of things you guys do that might be considered &quot;OCD&quot;? Myself I have a habit of requiring my paper money be all facing the same way in order from $1's (the innermost denomination) to, $5, $10, $20 and so forth. Plus I try to have them perfectly folded in half.

There's a few more things I have to have &quot;perfect&quot; but I want you to share yours!

Oh and on a side note. I think I have a job. Called this guy about working for him doing roofing tear off &amp; he called back today asking if I wanted to work Thursday. But I also have to call him back tonight to discuss further. Yay! It's been 9 fucking months since I had a real job. Unemployment had run out in May and the side jobs were not making ends meet at all! If I'm doing this for the rest of the summer I'll be one dark ass mofo.

